---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Captain Order POS & Retail ERP - End to End">

  <style>
    /* Gradient Text */
    .text-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #7c3aed, #4f46e5);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .bg-grid {
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                        linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    }
    
    html { scroll-padding-top: 100px; }
  </style>

  <section class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6 bg-slate-50 bg-grid border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 shadow-sm">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        KRA eTIMS Compliant ‚Ä¢ Anti-Theft Logic ‚Ä¢ Cloud Hybrid
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        The Operating System for <br />
        <span class="text-gradient">Kenyan Retail.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Stop revenue leakage. A specialized POS for <strong>Restaurants</strong>, <strong>Supermarkets</strong>, <strong>Pharmacies</strong>, and <strong>Hardware Stores</strong>. Track every gram of stock and every shilling of sales.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="#hospitality" class="bg-purple-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-purple-600/30">
          View Modules
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          Get Quote
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">KRA eTIMS</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Auto-Signing</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Inventory</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Recipe & Batching</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Payments</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">M-Pesa Integrated</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Security</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Blind Cash Drops</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="sticky top-[72px] z-40 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-y border-slate-200 py-4 hidden md:block">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">
      <a href="#hospitality" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Hospitality (KDS)</a>
      <a href="#retail" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Supermarket</a>
      <a href="#verticals" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Hardware & Pharmacy</a>
      <a href="#inventory" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Inventory</a>
      <a href="#reports" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Admin & Security</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section id="hospitality" class="py-24 px-6 bg-white border-b border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">üçΩÔ∏è</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Captain Order (Hospitality)</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Speed is everything. Eliminate handwritten chits and shouting orders. Connect your Waiters, Kitchen, and Cashier in one seamless loop.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-100 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-900 mb-2">Touch-Screen Waiter App</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-purple-700">Waiters take orders on a tablet/phone at the table. The order prints <strong>instantly</strong> at the Kitchen (Food) and Bar (Drinks) simultaneously.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
           <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Table Management</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Visual Map of your floor plan.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Color codes: <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">Free</span>, <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">Occupied</span>, <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">Billed</span>.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Merge Tables for large groups.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Split Bills for groups paying separately.</li>
              </ul>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Kitchen Display System (KDS)</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Digital screen replaces paper printers.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Track "Time to Serve" metrics.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Color alerts for delayed orders (>20 mins).</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ "Bump" orders when ready to notify waiter.</li>
              </ul>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Menu Engineering</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Modifiers: "No Onion", "Extra Cheese", "Well Done".</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Happy Hour: Auto-price change at 5 PM.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Combo Meals & Set Menus.</li>
              </ul>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Recipe Costing</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Define: 1 Burger = 1 Bun + 150g Meat + 20g Lettuce.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ System deducts raw materials upon sale.</li>
                 <li>‚Ä¢ Calculate Profit Margin per dish instantly.</li>
              </ul>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="retail" class="py-24 px-6 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div class="bg-slate-900 p-2 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
         <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/5">
            <div class="flex justify-between text-white border-b border-white/10 pb-4 mb-4">
               <div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Total Amount</div>
                  <div class="text-4xl font-bold font-mono">2,450.00</div>
               </div>
               <div class="text-right">
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Items</div>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-mono">14</div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 font-mono text-sm mb-6">
               <div class="flex justify-between text-slate-300">
                  <span>1x Brookside Milk 500ml</span>
                  <span>65.00</span>
               </div>
               <div class="flex justify-between text-slate-300">
                  <span>2x Jogoo Maize Meal 2kg</span>
                  <span>420.00</span>
               </div>
               <div class="flex justify-between text-slate-300">
                  <span>1x Blueband 500g</span>
                  <span>340.00</span>
               </div>
               <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs text-center py-2">... 11 more items ...</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
               <button class="bg-green-600 text-white py-3 rounded font-bold">CASH</button>
               <button class="bg-green-600 text-white py-3 rounded font-bold">M-PESA</button>
               <button class="bg-slate-700 text-white py-3 rounded font-bold">Hold Bill</button>
               <button class="bg-red-600 text-white py-3 rounded font-bold">Void Line</button>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">üõí</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Supermarket & Retail</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Designed for high-traffic environments. Process a sale in under 5 seconds with integrated barcode scanning and weighing scales.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
             <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Smart Shelf Labels</h4>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Generate and print Barcode/QR Code labels for shelves directly from the system. Update prices in bulk instantly.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
             <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Weighing Integration</h4>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Connect digital scales. System reads the barcode printed by the scale (embedding weight and price) automatically.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
             <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Loyalty Points</h4>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Retain customers with points per shilling spent. Redeemable for discounts on future purchases.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
             <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Wholesale & Retail Prices</h4>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Auto-switch prices based on quantity. Buy 1 @ KES 100, Buy 12 @ KES 90 (Wholesale Price).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="verticals" class="py-24 px-6 bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Specialized Business Modes</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg">We configured the logic for specific industries.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200">
           <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
             <span class="text-3xl">üî®</span> Hardware & Construction
           </h3>
           <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
             <li class="flex gap-3">
               <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 min-w-[120px]">Unit Conversion:</span>
               <span>Buy Cement in Tonnes, Sell in KGs. Buy Cable in Rolls, Sell in Meters. System handles the math.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex gap-3">
               <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 min-w-[120px]">Quotations:</span>
               <span>Generate proforma invoices for contractors. Convert to Invoice in one click upon payment.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex gap-3">
               <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 min-w-[120px]">Yard Collection:</span>
               <span>Customer pays at office, receives "Gate Pass". Warehouse releases goods only against Gate Pass.</span>
             </li>
           </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200">
           <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
             <span class="text-3xl">üíä</span> Pharmacy & Chemist
           </h3>
           <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
             <li class="flex gap-3">
               <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 min-w-[120px]">Expiry Management:</span>
               <span>Track Batch Numbers. System forces First-In-First-Out (FIFO) so old stock is sold first. Alerts 3 months to expiry.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex gap-3">
               <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 min-w-[120px]">Generic Linking:</span>
               <span>If "Brand X" is out of stock, system suggests "Generic Y" with same active ingredients.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex gap-3">
               <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 min-w-[120px]">Insurance Copay:</span>
               <span>Handle split payments: Insurance pays 80%, Patient pays 20% Cash/M-Pesa.</span>
             </li>
           </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="inventory" class="py-24 px-6 bg-slate-900 text-white border-b border-slate-800">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Advanced Inventory Control</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 text-lg">
          Know exactly what you have, what it costs, and when to re-order.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0">üöõ</div>
             <div>
               <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Procurement Cycle</h4>
               <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Requisition -> Purchase Order (LPO) -> Goods Received Note (GRN) -> Supplier Invoice.</p>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0">üìä</div>
             <div>
               <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Stock Take / Audits</h4>
               <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Perform partial stock takes via tablet. System highlights Variance (System vs Physical).</p>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0">üîÑ</div>
             <div>
               <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Inter-Branch Transfer</h4>
               <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Move stock between Warehouse and Branches. Track goods in transit.</p>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-700">
           <h4 class="text-purple-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-6">Stock Movement Logic</h4>
           <div class="space-y-4">
             <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</div>
               <div class="bg-slate-700/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-1 border border-slate-600">
                 <div class="font-bold text-sm">Purchase (GRN)</div>
                 <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Stock Increases. Weighted Average Cost updated.</div>
               </div>
             </div>
             <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</div>
               <div class="bg-slate-700/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-1 border border-slate-600">
                 <div class="font-bold text-sm">Recipe / Sale</div>
                 <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Stock Decreases based on BOM (e.g. 1 Coffee = 15g Beans + 200ml Milk).</div>
               </div>
             </div>
             <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</div>
               <div class="bg-slate-700/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-1 border border-slate-600">
                 <div class="font-bold text-sm">Re-Order Level</div>
                 <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">System sends Email to Manager when stock is critical.</div>
               </div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="reports" class="py-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Anti-Theft Intelligence</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500">Stop your staff from stealing. We log everything.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-red-100 text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üö´</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Void Control</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Cashiers cannot delete items from a bill without Manager Password/Card Override.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üëÅÔ∏è</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Audit Trail</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">See exactly who opened the cash drawer, at what time, and why. Logs printed bills vs reprints.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-green-100 text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üí∞</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Blind Cash Drops</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Cashiers declare cash *before* system shows expected amount. Any variance is flagged instantly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-slate-900 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Secure your business today.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-12">Join 500+ Retailers and Restaurants running on Captain Order POS.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-purple-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors">
          Request Quote
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/254715235119" class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
          WhatsApp Sales
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>